01:26:57.000 --> 01:26:58.740
It would still be true, right?

01:26:58.740 --> 01:27:01.440
That one doesn't--
one is, in a sense,

01:27:01.440 --> 01:27:03.600
better because it's
better than the other.

01:27:03.600 --> 01:27:06.840
But it doesn't dominate
