01:29:13.630 --> 01:29:17.560
And it turns out the bigger
your number of alternatives

01:29:17.560 --> 01:29:21.340
or architectures, the smaller
percentage-wise the set

01:29:21.340 --> 01:29:23.920
will be of
non-dominated solutions.

01:29:23.920 --> 01:29:27.270
And those are the ones you
really want to focus on.

